text: Pseudoechthistatus pufujiae is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bi and Lin in 2016. It is known from China.BioLib.cz - Pseudoechthistatus pufujiae. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 2016
